        <pagenum page="normal" id="pagenum_000003" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#pagenum_000003">1</pagenum>
        <p id="p_000029" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000029">The Moon</p>
        <p id="p_000030" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000030">and</p>
        <p id="p_000031" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000031">The Cap</p>
        <p id="p_000032" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000032">Written by</p>
        <p id="p_000033" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000033">Noni</p>
        <p id="p_000034" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000034">Illustrated by</p>
        <p id="p_000035" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000035">Angie &amp; Upesh</p>
        <pagenum page="normal" id="pagenum_000004" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#pagenum_000004">2</pagenum>
        <p id="p_000036" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000036">All of us went to the Dussera fair.</p>
        <p id="p_000037" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000037">This page contains the picture of two children going to Dussera along with their parents</p>
        <pagenum page="normal" id="pagenum_000005" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#pagenum_000005">3</pagenum>
        <p id="p_000038" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000038">Papa bought Chintu fancy glasses. Mother bought me a bright blue cap. The baby got sugar candy.</p>
        <p id="p_000039" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000039">This page contains the picture of two boys wearing fancy glass, cap and a girl having sugar candy.</p>
        <pagenum page="normal" id="pagenum_000006" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#pagenum_000006">4</pagenum>
        <p id="p_000040" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000040">On the way home, a very strong wind came. It blew my cap away.</p>
        <p id="p_000041" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000041">This page contains the picture of a boy whose cap is flying in the wind.</p>
        <pagenum page="normal" id="pagenum_000007" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#pagenum_000007">5</pagenum>
        <p id="p_000042" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000042">My cap got stuck on a branch of the old Pipal tree.</p>
        <p id="p_000043" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000043">This page contains the picture of cap sticking in the tree.</p>
        <pagenum page="normal" id="pagenum_000008" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#pagenum_000008">6</pagenum>
        <p id="p_000044" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000044">I cried a lot. And I did not eat my dinner.</p>
        <p id="p_000045" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000045">This page contains the picture of the boy crying and not eating the dinner.</p>
        <pagenum page="normal" id="pagenum_000009" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#pagenum_000009">7</pagenum>
        <p id="p_000046" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000046">Later that night the moon came up.</p>
        <p id="p_000047" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000047">It looked at my cap on the old Pipal tree.</p>
        <p id="p_000048" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000048">This page contains the picture of the boy looking cap through the window.</p>
        <pagenum page="normal" id="pagenum_000010" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#pagenum_000010">8</pagenum>
        <p id="p_000049" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000049">It tried on my cap. The moon smiled happily.</p>
        <p id="p_000050" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000050">I had to smile too.</p>
        <p id="p_000051" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000051">This page contains the picture of the moon smiling.</p>
        <pagenum page="normal" id="pagenum_000011" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#pagenum_000011">9</pagenum>
        <p id="p_000052" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000052">After school the next day, my mother gave me a shiny new red cap. "The moon sent it," she said.</p>
        <p id="p_000053" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000053">This page contains the picture of the boy holding a new red cap.</p>
        <pagenum page="normal" id="pagenum_000012" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#pagenum_000012">10</pagenum>
        <p id="p_000054" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000054">That night both the moon and I wore our caps and smiled. We were happy.</p>
        <p id="p_000055" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000055">This page contains the picture of the boy and moon wearing the cap.</p>
        <pagenum page="normal" id="pagenum_000013" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#pagenum_000013">11</pagenum>
        <p id="p_000056" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000056">Do you think the sun needs a hat?</p>
        <p id="p_000057" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000057">This page contains the picture of two boys looking at the sun.</p>
        <pagenum page="normal" id="pagenum_000014" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#pagenum_000014">12</pagenum>
        <p id="p_000058" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000058">Guess which cap I am wearing today!</p>
        <p id="p_000059" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000059">This page contains the picture of a boy with so many caps.</p>
        <pagenum page="normal" id="pagenum_000015" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#pagenum_000015">13</pagenum>
        <p id="p_000060" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000060">Hello, my name is Sonam Sonkar. I'm in class 8 and dream of being an engineer.</p>
        <p id="p_000061" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000061">I enjoy kathak and also love beautiful clothes.</p>
        <p id="p_000062" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000062">Thank you for buying this book. My friends and I will get to read many more books in our library because you bought this book.</p>
        <p id="p_000063" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000063">Noni is the pen name of a writer residing in Bangalore.</p>
        <p id="p_000064" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000064">She works in the field of education.</p>
        <p id="p_000065" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000065">Angie is a graphic designer and in her spare time loves to keep busy with ceramic. Upesh is an animator who collects graphic novels and catches up with odd films in his spare time. Together they form 'The Other Design Studio'.</p>
        <pagenum page="normal" id="pagenum_000016" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#pagenum_000016">14</pagenum>
        <p id="p_000066" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000066">Do you like to wear a cap on a sunny day?</p>
        <p id="p_000067" smilref="The_Moon_and_the_Cap00001.smil#p_000067">Find out who else likes to wear a cap in this charming book.</p>
